Cheers,

https://phoenix-dx.com/ and https://outsystems.education/

It is all working now.

Ok hi all, 

The https://labs.phoenix-dx.com/ version of the site is now accessible. The www.labs.phoenix-dx.com is not as it's missing a DNS record. 

If you need the www version of the site live, you will need to add this record:
www.labs.phoenix-dx.com to point to: labs.phoenix-dx.com

Let me know if you need anything else?
